{"_path":"/maps/_person/wu-qi","_dir":"_person","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"吴起","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"吴起"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"吴起"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"古籍"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"古籍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"史记七十列传孙子吴起列传"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://so.gushiwen.cn/guwen/bookv_46653FD803893E4F7319FE941E81F22F.aspx","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《史记·七十列传·孙子吴起列传》"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"起之为将，与士卒最下者同衣食。卧不设席，行不骑乘，亲裹赢粮，与士卒分劳苦。卒有病疽者，起为吮之。卒母闻而哭之。人曰：“子卒也，而将军自吮其疽，何哭为？”母曰：“非然也。往年吴公吮其父，其父战不旋踵，遂死於敌。吴公今又吮其子，妾不知其死所矣。是以哭之。”"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"古籍","depth":2,"text":"古籍"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:wu-qi.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/wu-qi.md","_extension":"md"}